CONTROLCAD
==========

 ControlCAD is managed throught the `initialize.bat` script. This script launch
 a Windows shell with all the settings adjusted in order to properly run the
 application. The available options are:

 runserver    Execute the WSGI web server at 127.0.0.1:8080 by default. This can
              be changed by passing an argument that contains the address and
              port in the form described above. ( e.g. 192.168.10:80 )

 shell        Execute the Django interactive shell, by default is IPython.

 database     Execute the SQLite database command line interface.

 Once the application is running type user `admin` and password `admin` in order
 to log into the administration panel.